<topic id="customizing_the_project_view">
    <title>Customizing the Project View</title>
    <body>
        <p>The API method
            <xref
                href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/InstData/Editor/SDK/javadoc/ro/sync/exml/workspace/api/standalone/StandalonePluginWorkspace.html#getProjectManager--"
                format="html" scope="external">StandalonePluginWorkspace.getProjectManager()</xref>
             allows access to various project-related functionality:
            <ul id="ul_ykm_xdj_rgb">
                <li>Add a new contextual menu action in the
                    <b>Project</b>
                     view.</li>
                <li>Access the set of resources currently selected in the
                    <b>Project</b>
                     view.</li>
                <li>Customize the icons which appear in the
                    <b>Project</b>
                     view.</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>A sample Javascript-based plugin using this API to add a new contextual menu to the
            Project view can be found here:
            <xref
                href="https://github.com/oxygenxml/wsaccess-javascript-sample-plugins/tree/master/OpenInTerminalProjectContextualAction"
                format="html" scope="external"/>
            .</p>
    </body>
</topic>
